,"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2010—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/4/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100(4)(A)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated pars. (2) to (12) as (3) to (13), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/4/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100(4)(B)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (1) and struck out former par. (1). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The term ‘Federal banking agencies’ means the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System, the Comptroller of the Currency, the Director of the Office of Thrift Supervision, the National Credit Union Administration, and the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/4/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100(4)(B)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (2). Former par. (2) redesignated (3)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Director” for “Secretary”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (10). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/4/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100(4)(C)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (10) and struck out former par. (10). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The term ‘Secretary’ means the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (11)(C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, § 1100(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Director” for “Secretary”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (12)(A)(ii). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s1100/2"},"text":